The Ironmaster Poster

An original un-used "proof" Video cover (8 1/2"x 11 3/4") for the 1983 Medusa release of the Italian prehistoric adventure "The Ironmaster" (1983). PLEASE note this was a PRE-CERT release. Artwork by Impressions.

This card cover has never been folded, has "SAMPLE" hole-punched to the lower left & is in excellent condition.
